{"tid":1602913,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好成日諗住10月1同班狗死過 呢啲大日子要對準政權","createTime":"2019-09-29T14:25:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T15:53:18.000Z","uid":290770,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"574c5ad9d07a0e3737c620b53fed404c5e76dd72","tid":1602913,"uid":290770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:25:24.000Z","msg":"大家好似唔記得左 我地每一次行動都要比個目標自己 好似71立法會612阻止二讀咁<br />\n次次都係淨係同班狗打其實無用 首先係武力唔對等 再者打贏左1次半次都其實影響唔到上面上上面<br />\n特別係十一呢啲大日子 再係平日咁樣嘅係無意思 之前都好似有人講過話外國記者開始走因爲唔想再報警民衝突<br />\n所以想提返大家之前提過嘅一個point 每次出去比個目標個日 立法會又好機場又好 而唔係為出而出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bfbadd57785c5cd66b92fdb36b7ab7e25f3f040","tid":1602913,"uid":282798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:26:27.000Z","msg":"個目標咪就係賀佢老母"},{"pid":"760e2b0976e049fd3c14f53be7de72984b5870f1","tid":1602913,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:26:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"69b404efa0423bfebca48b379ae9dc07bd6cdfdd","tid":1602913,"uid":290770,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9bfbadd57785c5cd66b92fdb36b7ab7e25f3f040","tid":1602913,"uid":282798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:26:27.000Z","msg":"個目標咪就係賀佢老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:27:29.000Z","msg":"我知 都要比啲目標去賀佢 好似71立法會612阻止二讀咁"},{"pid":"9cbf5b6b8e98e1e4df75fd9fb38fbf3d3f96fdb5","tid":1602913,"uid":290770,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:30:04.000Z","msg":"唉p牌又推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔想大家淨係諗住決一死戰"},{"pid":"1e6d6231f1d9f9dd28a27028d0d830d6f170835b","tid":1602913,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:05:03.000Z","msg":"屌你，唔同班狗死過點有下一步呀"},{"pid":"d71705b60d6b1d0f3d587873e0922ef546692fff","tid":1602913,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:05:13.000Z","msg":"見狗就打！"},{"pid"